snippet.description:
sub so I can hit 600k or you're banned. 

today we're doing Guess The Height! 5 people all with different heights and our job to match the height to the right person! 

TODAYS PANEL:
@hermanwrice 
@dennylove4real
@bradwilliamscomic
@morganjay


Have an idea for a video? submit it here: https://forms.gle/zFEDK99Bi9eWofzr5

Business Inquiries: max@millentertainment.com

Produced by @zanehelberg, he's a comedian and can be funny at times so feel free to go catch one of his shows if you're sad and need to laugh

Sound by Matt McC, he doesn't have social media but he does have beautiful long hair. 

DP was Ty aka NeedACameraMan! My boy got the best production team in the LA. 

Mandie is our main camera operator! She operates the close up so if she's whipping too fast, yall can go at her in the comments lmaoo she also does the coloring on the videos tho and she crushes it!

We also recently added Patrick aka @patstrongdog! he's our production coordinator but he truly does it all. All the mugs you see on the table, noteboooks, on air sign, etc... literally all the small stuff that make the videos 10x better, that's him!

Edited by Westley at Kid Robot! Westley lives in South Africa and was able to come onboard, learn my style and improve on it! If you're enjoying the edits show him some love in the comments! You're killing it Westley!!

all in a day's work.
